{{Flavour|A mighty old lich, notorious for blasting people with powerful conjurations at the slightest provocation, or just on a whim.}}

==Useful Info==
'''Master Blaster''' is the final boss of the Thunderdome [[Dungeon Sprint]] map.

<!--spl-bot-begin-->
==Spells==
{{Spellcaster
|number=
